 # SAVI Change Log - 2026-05-05
 
-## Profile Settings Beta Flow Polish
-
-- Created rollback archive:
-  `Docs/Design/ProfileArchive/2026-05-05-before-profile-beta-settings-polish/`.
-- Reworked the Profile header from generic `Profile` copy to `Your SAVI` with a
-  clearer settings/product framing.
-- Replaced the vague SAVI Beta card with a direct explanation: save from any
-  app, SAVI sorts it, and users can find it again by title, folder, tag, source,
-  or file type.
-- Added compact capability pills for `Share Sheet`, `Search`, `Private Vault`,
-  and `Full Archive`.
-- Added a `Set up SAVI` checklist with clear next steps for Share Sheet setup,
-  Private Vault protection, and full archive export.
-- Reorganized the visible Profile flow into: beta explanation, stats, setup,
-  manage, account/library, and small Social coming-soon note.
-- Updated Social Beta copy to be more explicit that Friends/public saves are
-  coming later, while this TestFlight keeps saves private.
-- Release iPhoneOS no-sign build passed:
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/profile-polish-release-iphoneos-nosign-20260505-104914.log`.
-- Captured Release simulator Profile screenshots in light and dark mode:
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/profile-polish-final-20260505-105004/profile-light.png`
-  and
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/profile-polish-final-20260505-105004/profile-dark.png`.
